        <mxCell id="c4SiLya5yYz-4mM6RkZj-5" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;p data-start=&quot;1067&quot; data-end=&quot;1116&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1) User should be able to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1094&quot; data-end=&quot;1116&quot;&gt;register and login&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1118&quot; data-end=&quot;1162&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2) User should be able to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1145&quot; data-end=&quot;1162&quot;&gt;upload videos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1164&quot; data-end=&quot;1208&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3) User should be able to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1191&quot; data-end=&quot;1208&quot;&gt;search videos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1210&quot; data-end=&quot;1277&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;4) User should be able to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1237&quot; data-end=&quot;1277&quot;&gt;watch videos in multiple resolutions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1279&quot; data-end=&quot;1287&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;360p ,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;480p ,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;720p ,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;1080p etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1319&quot; data-end=&quot;1361&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;5) User should be able to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1346&quot; data-end=&quot;1361&quot;&gt;like videos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1363&quot; data-end=&quot;1411&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;6) User should be able to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1390&quot; data-end=&quot;1411&quot;&gt;comment on videos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="350" width="530" x="-160" y="350" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
